| `cellKey` | Converts a Cell to a string key for Set/Map usage | Good -- clearly describes conversion to key |
| `parseKey` | Converts a string key back to a Cell | Good -- clear inverse of cellKey |
| `neighborsOf` | Returns all 8 neighbor coordinates of a cell | Good -- clearly reveals intent |
| `isNeighbor` | Checks if two cells are neighbors | Good -- clear predicate name |
| `countNeighbors` | Counts how many live cells are neighbors of a given cell | Adequate -- could be more specific (counts *live* neighbors) |
