1. Rename `countNeighbors` to `countLiveNeighbors` (Rule 2 - clarity)
2. Remove `isNeighbor` and rewrite `countLiveNeighbors` to use `neighborsOf` with a Set lookup (Rule 3 - no duplication, Rule 4 - fewer elements)

